<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Welcome!</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f9; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 24px; border-radius: 8px; }
      h1 { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      p { line-height: 1.5; }
      .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome, <%= @variables[:first_name] || 'there' %>!</h1>
      <p>
        We're excited to have you at Karya App. Your account has been created successfully.
      </p>
      <p>
        Use the platform to manage your tasks and stay productive. If you have any questions, just reply to this email.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="<%= @variables[:dashboard_url] || '#' %>" class="btn">Go to your dashboard</a>
      </p>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Karya App. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
